{* *! version 1.0.2  30may2019}{...}
{synopt :[{cmd:no}]{opt italic}}将文本格式化为斜体{p_end}
{synopt :[{cmd:no}]{opt bold}}将文本格式化为粗体{p_end}
{synopt :[{cmd:no}]{opt underl:ine}}在指定单元格中为文本加下划线{p_end}
{synopt :[{cmd:no}]{opt strike:out}}在指定单元格中将文本划掉{p_end}
{synopt :{cmd:script(sub}|{cmd:super}|{cmd:none)}}指定下标或上标格式{p_end}